          <div class='img-destaque position-relative overflow-hidden'>
            <img class='img-fluid' src='../app/assets/img/posts/destaques/68_mapa de empatia.png' alt='Imagem Destaque' />
          </div>
          <div class='content-blog position-relative overflow-hidden'>
            <div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Neste artigo, vamos discutir uma ferramenta amplamente utilizada por aqueles que desenvolvem ideias no </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">Avantt.i</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8">: o Mapa de Empatia. Descubra o que &eacute;, como funciona e quando deve ser utilizado no texto a seguir.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW261595338 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>O Mapa de Empatia &eacute; uma ferramenta &uacute;til para segmentar e entender melhor seu cliente. Ele permite identificar suas dores e necessidades reais e como o cliente enfrenta os problemas que sua ideia pretende resolver diariamente. Com essas informa&ccedil;&otilde;es, &eacute; poss&iacute;vel compreender os benef&iacute;cios que seu cliente busca, identificar oportunidades de neg&oacute;cio e ajudar a superar suas dores ou necessidades.</span></span></p>
<p class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="EOP SCXW261595338 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://inventta.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/a4-1024x512.png" width="682" height="341"></span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8">Quando usar o Mapa de Empatia?</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW261595338 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Antes de usar o Mapa de Empatia, &eacute; crucial realizar entrevistas e conversar com seus potenciais clientes para compreender o problema do ponto de vista deles, entendendo os ganhos e dores. Nesta fase inicial, &eacute; essencial entender os &ldquo;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">jobs</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">to</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">be</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">done</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8">&rdquo; dos clientes, ou seja, a jornada que eles percorrem em rela&ccedil;&atilde;o ao problema. Recomenda-se usar o </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">Customer</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8"> Profile (veja na imagem abaixo como preench&ecirc;-lo) antes de utilizar o Mapa de Empatia. Isso ajudar&aacute; a segmentar melhor seus clientes e identificar as personas com as quais voc&ecirc; est&aacute; trabalhando. A partir da&iacute;, utilize o Mapa de Empatia para consolidar as informa&ccedil;&otilde;es coletadas nas pesquisas, identificando os personagens que interagem com o problema e suas caracter&iacute;sticas espec&iacute;ficas.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW261595338 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="WACImageContainer NoPadding DragDrop BlobObject SCXW261595338 BCX8" role="presentation"><img class="WACImage SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="app/assets/img/posts/basepath/blobid1.jpg" alt="Customer Profile" width="609" height="385"></span></span><span class="EOP SCXW261595338 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8">Estrutura de um Mapa de Empatia</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW261595338 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>O Mapa de Empatia utiliza como base as informa&ccedil;&otilde;es obtidas em entrevistas com clientes. Para desenhar uma persona, al&eacute;m de considerar dores e necessidades, &eacute; importante explorar os sentidos, h&aacute;bitos e a&ccedil;&otilde;es dos entrevistados, categorizando-as da seguinte maneira:</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW261595338 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW261595338 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="20" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8">O que a pessoa pensa e sente?</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8"> Quais s&atilde;o os sentimentos e pensamentos da persona durante sua intera&ccedil;&atilde;o com o tema explorado pelo seu neg&oacute;cio? Quais s&atilde;o suas preocupa&ccedil;&otilde;es e aspira&ccedil;&otilde;es? Capture diferentes momentos e estados emocionais do usu&aacute;rio.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW261595338 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW261595338 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="20" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8">O que a pessoa v&ecirc; e ouve?</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8"> Quais s&atilde;o as influ&ecirc;ncias, influenciadores, marcas favoritas e produtos que essa persona consome? Quais s&atilde;o os ambientes de socializa&ccedil;&atilde;o e situa&ccedil;&otilde;es cotidianas dessa persona? Descreva as fontes de informa&ccedil;&atilde;o e observa&ccedil;&otilde;es do usu&aacute;rio relacionadas ao tema.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW261595338 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW261595338 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="20" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8">O que a pessoa fala e faz?</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8"> Quais s&atilde;o os comportamentos da persona? O que ela expressa e como? Quais s&atilde;o seus hobbies e atividades principais? Descreva as necessidades do usu&aacute;rio durante a execu&ccedil;&atilde;o dos seus &ldquo;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">jobs</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">to</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">be</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">done</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8">&rdquo; mencionados no </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">Customer</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8"> Profile.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW261595338 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW261595338 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="20" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="4" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8">Quais s&atilde;o as dores dessa pessoa?</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8"> Quais s&atilde;o os medos, obst&aacute;culos e frustra&ccedil;&otilde;es que a persona enfrenta nos seus &ldquo;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">jobs</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">to</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">be</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">done</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8">&rdquo;? Identifique as principais dores e pontos de inc&ocirc;modo do usu&aacute;rio.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW261595338 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW261595338 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="20" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="5" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8">Quais s&atilde;o os ganhos dessa pessoa?</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8"> Quais s&atilde;o as necessidades, desejos e benef&iacute;cios concretos que a persona busca? Descreva as necessidades do usu&aacute;rio durante a execu&ccedil;&atilde;o dos seus &ldquo;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">jobs</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">to</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">be</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">done</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8">&rdquo; mencionados no </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW261595338 BCX8">Customer</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8"> Profile.</span></span> <span class="EOP SCXW261595338 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p><span class="EOP SCXW261595338 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://inventta.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/mapa-de-empatia.still_-1024x573.png" alt="Mapa de Empatia" width="817" height="457"></span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8">&nbsp;</p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>E depois?</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW261595338 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Ap&oacute;s aprofundar seu conhecimento sobre o cliente utilizando o Mapa de Empatia, &eacute; necess&aacute;rio colocar a solu&ccedil;&atilde;o desenhada pelo seu neg&oacute;cio no mercado para teste e valida&ccedil;&atilde;o com o cliente real. Verifique se a solu&ccedil;&atilde;o resolve os problemas identificados, se os clientes percebem valor na solu&ccedil;&atilde;o e se est&atilde;o dispostos a aderir e pagar por ela. &Eacute; importante destacar que essa valida&ccedil;&atilde;o busca confirmar as hip&oacute;teses de desejabilidade e proposta de valor da solu&ccedil;&atilde;o. Al&eacute;m disso, outros dois tipos de valida&ccedil;&atilde;o s&atilde;o essenciais na etapa de teste: a viabilidade econ&ocirc;mica e a viabilidade t&eacute;cnica. Para mais detalhes sobre a valida&ccedil;&atilde;o de solu&ccedil;&otilde;es inovadoras, consulte o artigo &ldquo;Validando a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o&rdquo;.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW261595338 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW261595338 BCX8">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW261595338 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="TextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW261595338 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW178420400 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW236060174 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Agora que voc&ecirc; entende a import&acirc;ncia de ter empatia com seus clientes, est&aacute; na hora de conversar com eles para validar sua ideia!</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW261595338 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;<br></span></p>
<h3>Sobre a Avantt.i&nbsp;</h3>
<p><span class="TextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>A Avantt.i &eacute; uma plataforma de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o desenvolvida pela Inventta, para gestores de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o e gerentes de projeto.</p>
<p><span class="TextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Com m&oacute;dulos de intra, open e gest&atilde;o do portf&oacute;lio, oferecemos uma vis&atilde;o completa da Gest&atilde;o da Inova&ccedil;&atilde;o para alavancar suas iniciativas.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Vis&atilde;o global e gest&atilde;o do portf&oacute;lio: </strong>Atrav&eacute;s da consolida&ccedil;&atilde;o do portf&oacute;lio de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o, a Avantt.i ajuda a identificar os principais projetos e avan&ccedil;ar com assertividade. Tudo em uma &uacute;nica plataforma.&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Programa de intra: </strong>Crie desafios e obtenha participa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos colaboradores. A inova&ccedil;&atilde;o vira rotina e voc&ecirc; impulsiona a cultura de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o na empresa.</li>
<li><strong>Open Innovation:</strong> Chame startups e parceiros para desafios, gerencie parceria na plataforma e tenha acesso a mais de 23.000 startups na nossa base.</li>
<li><strong>M&eacute;tricas Acion&aacute;veis: </strong>Influencie a organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o a investir em esfor&ccedil;os de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o com base em m&eacute;tricas claras e acion&aacute;veis. Me&ccedil;a resultados dos projetos e comunique o sucesso das iniciativas</li>
<li><strong>Inova&ccedil;&atilde;o Integrada e Transparente: </strong>Gerencie projetos de diferentes esteiras e horizontes, com colabora&ccedil;&atilde;o de parceiros e equipe, visualizando o portf&oacute;lio globalmente.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
